Priority: optional
Maintainer: Cplus Shen <cplus.shen@advantech.com.tw>
Build-Depends: cmake, debhelper (>=11~)
Standards-Version: 4.1.4
Homepage: http://www.advantech.com.tw/

Package: hdcp
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: The Intel unified HDCP server and client.
 The hdcp package is a user space implementation to prevent
 copying of digital audio & video content across digital
 display interfaces. It provides Linux user space
 implementation to enable the HDCP1.4 and HDCP2.2 protection
 for external digital display interfaces (HDMI/DP).
